a.org/Person"><h2 class="author-title">About the author</h2><div id="author-avatar"> <img itemprop="image" style="display:none;" src="http://gravatar.com/avatar/98a5deec648781958be7c6f65a6986f4" alt="" /> <img src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2008/04/Francesco-116x200.jpg" width="58" height="100" alt="Francesco Giudiceandrea" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 alignnone photo" /></div><div id="author-description" class="padding-20"><meta itemprop="name" content="Francesco Giudiceandrea"><meta itemprop="url" content=""><p></p><p class="add-author-info"> <a href="#"><i class="icon-facebook-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-twitter-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-google-plus-sign"></i></a></p> <a style="font-size: 11px;" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/francesco-giudiceandrea/">View all articles by Francesco Giudiceandrea</a></div></div><div class="nav-block box-shadow-2px padding-20 clearfix"> <nav class="nav-single"><h3 class="assistive-text">Post navigation</h3> <span class="nav-previous"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2010/12/new-york-metropolitan-operala-fanciulla-del-west/" rel="prev"><span class="meta-nav">&larr;</span> New York, Metropolitan Opera:&#8221;La fanciulla del West&#8221;</a></span> <span class="nav-next"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2010/12/dai-doppi-finali-alle-edizioni-anastatiche-alcune-considerazioni-in-merito-alla-tradizione-de-lorfeo/" rel="next">Dai doppi finali alle edizioni anastatiche. Alcune considerazioni in merito alla tradizione de LOrfeo (prima parte) <span class="meta-nav">&rarr;</span></a></span> </nav><nav class="nav-single-hidden"> <span class="nav-previous"></span> <span class="nav-next"></span><div class="clear"></div> </nav></div><div class="comments-block box-shadow-2px clearfix"><div id="comments" class="comments-area"><h2 class="comments-title"> 1 comment</h2><ol class="commentlist"><li class="comment even thread-even depth-1" id="li-comment-6120"> <article id="commen